<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6%E8%80%85.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6%E8%80%85.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>生物学家</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上的、包含下列任一标签的SCP文档：生物性、活物、基因、动物、植物、细菌</strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="right-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E8%80%85.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E8%80%85.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>物理学家</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上的、包含下列任一标签的SCP文档：反物理定律、反熵、电力、磁性、重力影响</strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="left-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E8%80%85.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E8%80%85.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>心理学家</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上的、包含下列任一标签的SCP文档：精神影响、模因、强迫性、移情作用、记忆影响、知识</strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="right-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E6%97%85%E4%BA%BA.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E6%97%85%E4%BA%BA.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>旅行家</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上的、包含下列任一标签的SCP文档：时空、未来、超维度、地图、门径</strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="right-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%B4%A9%E5%A3%8A%E3%81%AE%E3%81%8D%E3%81%A3%E3%81%8B%E3%81%91.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%B4%A9%E5%A3%8A%E3%81%AE%E3%81%8D%E3%81%A3%E3%81%8B%E3%81%91.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>梦想是毁灭世界</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上、包含K级情景标签的SCP文档</strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="right-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E6%98%A0%E7%94%BB%E3%81%A8%E3%81%8B%E3%81%A7%E5%BE%8C%E3%82%8D%E3%81%AE%E6%96%B9%E3%81%AB%E3%81%84%E3%82%8B%E3%83%A2%E3%83%96.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E6%98%A0%E7%94%BB%E3%81%A8%E3%81%8B%E3%81%A7%E5%BE%8C%E3%82%8D%E3%81%AE%E6%96%B9%E3%81%AB%E3%81%84%E3%82%8B%E3%83%A2%E3%83%96.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>哈？就这？</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上、关于Explained级项目的SCP文档</strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="left-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%83%8B%E3%83%A5%E3%83%BC%E3%83%88%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A4%E3%82%B9%E3%83%89.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%83%8B%E3%83%A5%E3%83%BC%E3%83%88%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A4%E3%82%B9%E3%83%89.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>全部木大</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上、关于Neutralized级项目的SCP文档</strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="left-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%B8%B8%E8%AD%98%E5%A4%96%E3%82%8C.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%B8%B8%E8%AD%98%E5%A4%96%E3%82%8C.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>这个东西我不能跟你解释</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上、关于未分级项目的SCP文档</strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="right-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E8%AD%9A.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E8%AD%9A.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>不是X战警！</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上的、以具有自我的，外貌类似人类的人型项目为主角的故事</strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="right-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E9%80%B1%E5%88%8A%E8%AA%8C.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E9%80%B1%E5%88%8A%E8%AA%8C.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>拒绝咕咕咕</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>一个月内发布4篇以上的文档</strong></span></p>
</div>
<hr /></div>
</div>
